actions.text: Measure failed of passage in House under suspension of rules, roll call #721 (169-95).

official_title: Resolution providing for agreeing to the Senate amendment to the House amendment to S. 921, with an amendment.

summary.text: Provides that immediately upon the adoption of this resolution the bill S. 921, with the Senate amendment to the House amendment thereto, be taken from the Speaker's table to the end that the Senate amendment to the House amendment be agreed to with an amendment as follows: In lieu of the matter proposed to be inserted by the Senate amendment, insert the text of the bill H.R. 12128.

titles.title: Resolution providing for agreeing to the Senate amendment to the House amendment to S. 921, with an amendment.
